   WASHINGTON -- Avondale Industries Inc. was issued a $104.4
million Navy contract for an oceanographic survey ship.
                                                                                                       

</LP>
<TEXT>
   McDonnell Douglas Corp. received awards of $18.2 million
for Army helicopter parts and Air Force jet engine flight
tests.
                                                                                                       

   General Electric Co. got a $17 million Navy pact for
submarine communications.
                                                                                                       

