<IN>
TENDER OFFERS, MERGERS, ACQUISITIONS (TNM)
</IN>
<LP>
   BFS Bankorp Inc. backed a plan under which Fredric H.
Gould, Gould Investors L.P. and BRT Realty Trust would seek
clearance to boost their stake in the thrift to as much as
24.9% from 9.9%.
   BFS also agreed to expand its board to six members from
