million, for BFS, which rejected the bid as inadequate. The
Redondo Beach, Calif., investment firm waged a proxy fight,
and one of its executives was named to BFS's board. BFS filed
suit to block First Capital from making any offer and to void
any proxies that First Capital solicited.
   A spokesman for First Capital was unavailable for comment.
